1. The Lois Lane of the Future! (Superman's Girlfriend, Lois Lane)

2. Ambush at Sundown (Johnny Thunder)

3. The Fantastic Fish that Defeated Aquaman (Aquaman and Aqualad)

4. The Jungle Circus (Congo Bill and Janu)

5. The Duel of Doom

6. Canyon of Whirling Death (Hopalong Cassidy)

7. Rex, Dinosaur Destroyer (Rex the Wonder Dog)

8. The Theatre of a Thousand Thrills

9. Thanksgiving Day--1990 (Atomic Knights)

10. Dr. Floogle (Gag strip by Henry Boltinoff)

11. Jimmy Olsen, Wolf-Man (Superman's Pal, Jimmy Olsen)

12. Mystery Message from Fort Nova

13. The Brain-Pirates of Planet X (Captain Comet)
name: The Lois Lane of the Future!

description:
Boots Heels Claws

Clawed-Agent and the She-Agent go head to head with New York's number one citizen, Dante Lazarus, when the Boom-Operator crashes the party. How will CA & SA save themselves without destroying the city in the process?
name: Mr & Mrs Agent

description: So, in the last issue Nessi and Norfus set up Tuesday and her crew, leading them to a back alley street fight with the Loveland Frogs. This issue will see Tuesday, Pigstein, and Robert continue their investigation on the mugging of Stan the goatman. We meet a doctor who puts McDreamy to shame! Plus, a HUGE fight scene with big guns and a Kaiju!

Deadly Silence Part 1

The Guardians are called upon to help stop an assassin of incredible skill. Will they be able to though? Or will this assassin be too much?
name: Deadly Silence Part 1

description:
Birth of Venus Part 1

Mario Simone presents the next installment in the Heroes Haven comic series, The Birth of Venus, Part One. When a professional hitman named Mr. Smith is taken from the streets of L.A. and brought to Heroes Haven, he is forced to undergo the excruciating experimental process designed to awaken his latent superhero abilities. While the procedure is a success, Smith's mind is shattered. Returned to the mean L.A. streets, Mr. Smith is a tortured soul barely able to contain his primal rage within. There is only one woman who can shed light on Smith's condition and her name is Starletta...
name: Birth of Venus Part One

description:
LA Underground

Detective Martinez learns more about "The Tower of the Book," even as her Angel partner Pyr'ell deals with rising conflicts on the streets of L.A. Meanwhile Alex delves deeper and deeper into Old Santa Monica to discover a terrifying truth.
name: Paradise High Part Three of Five: LA Underground

description: The Justice Purveyors want to up their superhero game...so they hire a Super Life Coach!!
name: Super Life Coach

volume.name: The Misadventures of Electrolyte and The Justice Purveyors

description:
The Worm Part 2

The Matador concocts a desperate plan for a desperate situation. But will it be enough to save his new allies from the worm monster that has set its sights on their underground compound?
name: The Worm Part 2

description: Lost and alone, Abigail takes shelter in an old cabin. Tea is had and and snares are sprung.

No Rest, No Peace

Five years ago the superhero known as Psypher sacrificed himself to stop the terrorist called Living Nightmare. Nightmare was arrested and Psypher was given a hero's funeral. Now somebody else has taken up the mantle of Psypher. The new Psypher so far has defeated the returned Living Nightmare and battled a man who was able to control gravity. People start to warm up to the idea that a new Psypher is now in their lives and the news constantly cover his exploits. But the real question is: Who is the new Psypher?
name: No Rest, No Peace

description:
Softening the Stone

The holidays can be a stressful time, especially when trying to bring two families together. The Odysseys try to spend a peaceful holiday as the guests of their CIA bodyguard John's family in Tokyo, Japan. However, old wounds get reopened and some truths come to light as the two families attempt to make it through the holidays without killing each other. On top of that, a giant demon cat is terrorizing the city of Tokyo during New Years. Please enjoy this holiday story by Greathouse and Leonard.
name: Softening the Stone

description: The Albert Hills Satanic Congregation has pinned all their hopes on black metal heroes Hëll Hëlm, but, when the band arrives from Norway they are not what the everyone expected. Carrion crows are circling above. From the shadows, Jezabelle Sixsmith and her new coven are working evil magics. If Hëll Hëlm can't save the church, who can?

Chapter 15

Jeff is worried that his friend Connor knows he's a werewolf.
name: Chapter 15

description:
Nova

Emily is back in the belly of the beast. Will old loyalties sway her new allegiance?
name: Nova

description:
The Ghost of Logging's Past

Big Red McLane's cannibal nemesis Liver Eatin' Johnson has returned--but he has bigger things on his mind, like taking his supervillain wife to meet his mother. And after years of careful planning the master plan of the Church of Paul Bunyan has finally begun it's endgame.
name: The Ghost of Logging's Past

description:
76 pages of Astounding Action-Packed Arachnid-Adventure! Only £3.50!

Spiral begins! A new spider-saga from comic legend Gerry Conway! Spider-Man fights side-by-side with Wraith!

Plus, Spider-Man 2099 and Doctor Strange at the mercy of the malevolent Maestro!

Also, fresh from the pages of Spider-Verse, Spider-Gwen returns to battle the vile Vulture!

By Gerry Conway, Carlo Barberi, Peter David, Will Sliney, Jason Latour and Robbi Rodriguez!

Includes material reprinted from Amazing Spider-Man #16.1, Spider-Man 2099 #10 and Spider-Gwen #!

76 pages of Earth's Mightiest Heroes!

The 'Axis' saga explodes! Avenger battles Avenger! The X-Men ally themselves with Apocalypse! What the heck is going on?!

By Rick Remender, Leinil Francis Yu, Al Ewing and Luke Ross!

Featuring material first printed in Axis #4-5 and Captain America & The Mighty Avengers #2-3.

Young Ora, an Orphan Elf, is divided between her desire for revenge and the tragic fate of the Elf people who once abandoned her.

Ora, a young Elf brought up by the Orcs, has become a warrior and wants to prove to all that she is worthy of the clan. She decides to take revenge on the person who killed

her parents and chased her out of her forest: Eliseii, Queen of the Elves. But to kill her would condemn the Forest people to certain death because, all around them, men are dying under the fangs of monsters from the North… before coming back to life, starving and malicious!
name: La Reine des Sylvains

description:
A particulary spectacular album that sees the great accomplishment of Darko’s fate!

Demons keep coming out of the Haven of Light and infiltrate the Five Kingdoms. Even the powerful wizard Kamphre cannot stop the continuous stream. Darko, Tara, Urfold and Sleilo are training peoples of the forests to

eradicate the demons but it is within the Haven itself that the door can be closed. Darko decides to try all whilst Kamphre calls upon the most powerful demon of the lower circles…
name: Un Flot de Lumiere

description:
76 pages of gamma-powered action!

Doc Green has the Red She-Hulk in his sights! A shocking secret is revealed as the two gamma-powered beings battle! By Gerry Duggan and Mark Bagley!

She-Hulk goes head-to-head with Daredevil – in court! And Captain America's legacy is at stake! By Charles Soule and Javier Pulido!

The Hulk battles Thanos and the forces of Annihilus! More amazing cosmic action by Jim Starlin!

Featuring material first printed in Hulk #8, She-Hulk #9 and Thanos vs Hulk #2-3.

100-page special!

Deadpool clashes with Blade as an epic new adventure begins! Don't miss 'Dracula's Gauntlet' by Gerry Duggan, Brian Posehn and Reilly Brown!

Wolverine returns to Madripoor, on the trail of Sabretooth! By Paul Cornell and Ryan Stegman!

Featuring material first printed in Wolverine #5-6 and Deadpool: Dracula's Gauntlet #1-2.

name: Buck Jones e o Bandido Branco

description:
THE CONTAGION HAS JUST BEGUN...

Nothing stops the walking dead. Town by town, the advance and devour the living. However, the developed nations don't really realize the level of danger. La Pointe, B series Canadian actor, keeps living like nothing is going on. Honorary guest to a horror movie festival, he fi nds himself trapped, alone in zombie territory. He understands that he has nothing of a hero when reality joins fiction. Today, there are no more scenarios, doubles or special effects, however he must play the part of his life.
name: La Mort et le Mourant

description:
THE DEATHLY FACE-OFF BETWEEN HUMANS AND ZOMBIES.

The human being is no longer on top of the food chain. Zombies stole its place and nothing seems to be able to stop them. Is this the end of humanity? Maybe not... for some it's just a new beginning. Sam ran from the big cities and left his daughter behind. However, now that silence and desolation reign over the United States, he still believes she is alive... He must find her; that is the only way he will survive.
name: De la brièveté de la vie

description:
THE ZOMBIES ARE COLONIZING THE WORLD AND NOTHING SEEMS TO BE ABLE TO STOP THEM...

On the west coast of the United States, millions of zombies are piling up around the island colonized by the survivors of the boat caravan. What should have been paradise turns into hell but the community led by Serge LaPointe, the old horror film actor, refuses to give up. East, a new daily life without zombies is emerging. A genius from Boston, Clay Harris, found a way to get rid of the zombies and if there is anyone to save, even on the other side of the country, he is making it his business to do so and get the American dream back on track.
name: Précis de décomposition

description:
What happened during the last thirty years so that a wind abandoned by life carries away the hopes and dreams of distant times?

Thirty years have passed since the appearance of the virus. The devastated United States have become the domain of a handful of nomads immunised against Death itself. The zombies

have almost disappeared, but the pilgrims of this new world do not build anything, they are just waiting for the end. Mankind does, however, have a chance of getting out of the problem thanks to the thousands of survivors who sought refuge in Boston and Iceland…
name: Les Moutons

volume.name: Bonanza: Suplemento ao Mundo de Aventuras

name: Die wilde Hilde: Eine Hexe dreht durch

person_credits.name: Jack T. Chick
person_credits.role: writer, penciler, letterer, inker, colorist, cover, production

person_credits.name: George Herriman
person_credits.role: writer, penciler, letterer, inker, colorist, cover

description:
Kenneth the Conjuror

The Conjuror battles Slush and Snowflake on the streets of downtown Sunflower Hills. Issue Zero presents the 8-page story where the Conjuror made his first appearance. This story incorporates into the ongoing adventures as the events between Issues 2 and 3.
name: Kenneth the Conjuror

person_credits.name: Rumiko Takahashi
person_credits.role: writer, penciler, letterer, inker, colorist, cover

description:
Collects Chapters 9-17 of the Harvey Award nominated adventure series.

Albert the Alien is the first foreign exchange student from space -- and someone is trying to get him expelled! All of the teachers have mysteriously called in sick, and been replaced by robot substitute teachers. It's up to Albert and his friends to figure out who's trying to take over the school, and stop them before they ruin Homecoming.
name: Vol. 2

volume.name: Albert the Alien: The Substitute Teacher From Planet X

description:
Venice, 1510. The great painter Giorgione is dying of the plague. He expends a final burst of energy finishing his last piece, a pictorial homage to his first romantic emotion.

Giorgione also must face the question all painters ask themselves, how to bring to life the extraordinary image of a presence on a completely flat surface?

Antonello in Venice is a complete story.

In Mayber Hills Sanitarium secrets haunt the hallways and words must not be spoken. Obleena Grunkel aka "Bleen" finds herself locked within the doors of the facilities along with her bunny friend Mr. Wiggles. At the mercy of twisted staff members, will she end up another victim of the games, or will her own dark secret come to life from underneath her bed to claim it's own victims?

Collects Bleen #1-4.

Smashing the mercenary fun of the A-Team with misfit nature Archer & The Venture Bros., B-Squad takes a squad of misfit mercenaries on ridiculous & dangerous adventures killing off squad-members every issue! A half-dozen artists bring to life the first 5 adventures with B-Squad facing off against insurance-fraud fearing hipsters, a crazy masking tape wizard, a dachshund-fueled monsters, and the rogue A.I. of a British nuclear submarine.
name: Vol. 1

description: A heroic tomboy stumbles into the role of "magical girl," in a quest where navigating a world full of frilly dresses, jewelry and fairies will be the only way to save the world from the ambitions of an evil sorceress.

Sneak Peek

Dark Ocean is a contemporary supernatural story, where a couple accidentally gets in touch with the spiritual world, revealing a universe unknown to us.

Druid Fluid Issue One

Tunnel through a cascade of surreal images and an unstoppable dreamlike narrative flow on your journey through a back alley tour to erotic adult fantasy. For mature readers only!

Volume 1: Player's Handbook

The adventures of Fili (a Fighter) and Noli (a Wizard), in high fantasy hubris and idiocy.

This collection of comic strips first appeared online at favouritecrayon.co.uk, and is packed full of #MMO #RPG #metahumour.
name: Volume 1: Player's Handbook

volume.name: Experience the Magic of the Legend!

description: The Fall of Ebla is an historical adventure about the conquest of ancient Sumer by King Sargon of Akkad during the early bronze age. His ascent to power exerted supreme reign over mankind, and the expansion of his empire to the four corners of the world would boast a dominance that was unparalleled by any other ruler of his era. The account is retold through the eyes of the royal scribe of Ebla, and his faithful slave Ahuni, as King Sargon and his warrior grandson Naram-Sin leads a gruesome Akkadian attack on the peaceful Sumerian city of Ebla.

Drawn in delicate ink and bright watercolors, Fox Head Stew mixes glam rock, psychedelic powers, and self-discovery through art classes, guitar lust, booze, and one-night-stands. Sam finds escape from his depression by playing music, while Dee tries to hide her strange inner-self through college parties, drinking, and getting lost in private, hallucinatory flights-of-fancy. Float along as Dee's daily life gets distorted with lucid fantasies, strange creatures, vivid music and gorgeous daydreams in Jamaica Dyer's original take on the quarter-life crisis.

saviors

A farmer's life turns tragic when a monster destroys his home killing his family. Hell bent in revenge, he heads into the mountains to confront the creature.
name: Saviors

description:
Young Steno Critone doesn't want to stop dreaming. In a world where no one has the time to try something that isn't already provided by the system, Steno fears that his dreams will one day die. He has no idea that the fate of the world relies on his ability to dream.

Set in a future, post-Eurozone Italy, entrenched in a culture of hyper-capitalism, GOLEM follows young Steno Critone as he is kidnapped during a political protest gone sour. Taken in by the band of labeled "terrorists," he learns that things are not as they seem in society, and that he has the power to not only change the city, but reality itself.

This intensely imaginative political-sci-fi graphic novel is a visual tour de force, created by contemporary design icon Lorenzo Ceccotti, better known as LRNZ, whose design-influenced illustration provides a lush, fluid backdrop of maga-like dynamism with the cinematic scope of western comics, creating a style that is wholly unique and absolutely breathtaking.

Idle Hands Comix by Paul R Cheshire.

'Immature content for mature readers.'.

Idle Hands Comix is an original comic by London based Writer & Artist Paul R Cheshire featuring Puerile Ghosts, NSA Trolls & Petty Djinns .

Fifteen years ago, magical girl Shimmer Shimmer Sky Patcher Chimaka lost her final battle against her greatest foe, broke up with her "destined" boyfriend, and practically flunked out of school. Now a chemical engineer at Squid Petroleum, Chimaka is older, wiser, and a whole lot more bitter. But when her ancient enemy grows restless again, it's up to Chimaka and her best friend Pippa to try to reignite Chimaka's old magic...and save the world!
name: Magical Woman Chimaka

description:
Making the Monster

A dark tale of the madness that loss brings, based on Lance Roth's short story, "Nothing Contributes So Much to Tranquilize the Mind."

A down and out con artist named Dominick Hanson A.K.A. 'Vill Inn' (as he's known to his peers) is down on his luck. He owes a large sum of money to a dangerous gangster and if he doesn't pay it's the end of him.

As he sits at the bar trying to figure things out. He takes notice of a young female fighter named Natalie Means. A fighter whos brashness and arrogance is only exceeded by her appetite and talent for fighting.

He decides he's going to use her for a con to get the money he owes. Little does he know he is about to find a legend.

The Mick is the story of Sean Doyle, the Chief of Staff of the Irish Republican Army in the late 1930s. World War Ii is happening in Europe and the struggle to create an Irish Republic is at the forefront of the Ira's agenda. To win a war of physical force and propaganda against the British Empire, he finds himself in New York City and in more trouble than Doyle could have ever counted on. Based upon a true story, The Mick is a hard boiled tale of terrorists, gangsters, corrupt politicians, crooked cops, and Nazis.

The Toy From Out of This World

After getting chewed out by his boss, Toy designer Abe has to whip up new design by tomorrow morning or he's out of the job. The pressure is on when an alien baby crashes through his living room and calls him "mama".
name: The Toy From Out of This World

description:
Two soldiers. A Pledge. The Adventure.

Within the WWI trench, a French aristocrat officer, Calixte de Prampéand, and a Corsican soldier, Léon Matilo, make a deal. If they survive, they will turn into pirates and sail over the sea. Three years later, léon pays a visit to Calixte : there is business opening in arms dealing and I want you in. But beware, if you leave to gain your freedom, there is no way back...
name: Call of the Open Sea

description:
The Double and the Duchess

Creeo ends up upsetting the balance in a war between a human King Samuel, those rebelling against him and an advancing horde of orcs and ogres.
name: The Double and the Duchess

volume.name: On the Brink of the Universe

description:
Matthew Marshalls must face his past to become the superstar he wants to be. But to do that, he must become a superhero! Is he destined to become the Street Sweepah? Or just more trash to be taken out?

Matthew Marshals has come to a crossroad of his life: become a superstar rapper or take on the family business of sweeping the streets.

Princess Lucinda Nightbane had it all. She had servants, a loving family and magical powers. It was a perfect, life any twelve year old girl would envy...up until the rebellious forces of good and light attacked!

Princess Lucinda: The Black Rose of the Empire chronicles the origin, and first adventure of everyone's favorite wicked princess as her life is turned upside down in part one of a three part epic story of loss, revenge, and change.

Issue 1 contains;

  • An epic 64 page comic book style story
  • Gallery by some of the hottest new artist around
  • Appendix detailing background information about Lucinda's world and family history.
name: Book One: Black Rose of the Empire

description: Warren Ellis' brilliant crime epic is collected in this incredible graphic novel. How much of a monster do you have to become to hunt monsters? John Cain has been working Homicide long enough to get hard to pretty much anything; even wrenching personal loss. But everyone has a limit, and today it's gotten too much to bear. Today, he gets assigned something that finally breaks through his defenses - a child killing that hits horribly close to home. Until today, he's been a good cop, a cop who goes by procedure because it's the best way to ensure that scum go to prison. Now, he makes the parents of the victim a chilling promise: he will find the killer using any means necessary. And the killer will not get away with it - no matter what it takes!
name: TPB

description:
WHO IS THE SHAMAN? In a world where great heroes and villains die every day, the Shaman is the one who brings them back. But sometimes...things get complicated.

A young superhero, the Vanisher, has just seen his grandfather rise from the grave as a crazed, teleporting skeleton. If this is one of the Shaman's mistakes, will he help put the rampaging bag of bones back to rest?

And hey, what's the deal with that girl's tattoos?

Tai Wu Xia the Ultimate Kung Fu Warrior is a young Chinese superhero. Harry Chen, his alter ego in whom powers are combined in ways never seen before, finally comes to terms with his special super powers and training in tai chi and kung fu to take up the mantle to fight bad guys and evil that threaten China, and even the rest of the world.

Harry Chen is the thirteenth generation in both families of tai chi and kung fu masters. Long before his birth, and even before his parents knew each other, fortune tellers on either side of his family predict that, "In the fullness of time, a boy, of the thirteenth generation of your family, shall be born in the year of the sheep. He may be weak and powerless, and the one to bring an end to the family's long line of mastery. Or, he could mark the beginning of an even more powerful dispensation of your lineage, as in him powers may be combined in ways never seen before. His final destiny shall, in part, lie in the hands of his ancestors and in part in his own."

As Providence would have it, Harry is born in the year of the sheep. But ancestors on both sides of the family are not going to stand by helplessly as the first part of the prophecy comes to pass. At the time of his birth, they gather around and call upon their favourite gods of ancient times to give them certain powers which they plant into the child together with the seeds of tai chi and kung fu skills which they honed over centuries, ensuring that the part of the prophecy that says "he could mark the beginning of an even more powerful dispensation of your lineage," is instead fulfilled. Thus begins the making of Tai Wu Xia.
name: Fu the Immortal

volume.name: Tai Wu Xia - Ultimate Kung Fu Warrior

description:
TJ Riprovare has it all. Popularity, schoolwork and sports all come easy to him. His band has even been offered a contract! But when a mysterious stranger tells him his whole life is a lie, TJ starts to question how much is real, and must confront the cause of all his problems - his father.

Takes One to Know One is an occasionally dark, sometimes humorous story that will make you question the motives of all the relationships in your own life.

« Allow me to tickle your fancies with my tale, a tale woven from the threads of a hundred other tales... ». These are the very first words of a smart and masked storyteller.

His story tells how Irvi, an odd and acrobatic young man, tries to free Sian, a beautiful virgin sold by her own parents, called to join the Princess House. But Faith has other plan.
name: The Lovers

volume.name: Tales from the Time of the Cobra

description: Task Force Rad Squad #1 is 32 pages of full-color calamity that introduces readers to three teens with rad-ditude, their potion-addled new "mentor" and the weary AI known as Ph.R.A.N.C.I.S. Powered by the specious cosmic tech of an extinct Space Wizard civilization, the team has inherited a universe of messes (not limited to evil birthday cakes) they rightfully resent having to mop up. But who knows? Maybe conquering adversity as a team will teach them the true meaning of friendship? Or maybe they'll unlock the secret history of the universe, discover their place in existence and embrace their collective destiny as humanity's one last shot at survival?

A modern, dark and violent Arabian Nights Tale

They call him Kabyle. He was an Assassins. He then became a Jinn, locked up in a Lamp. Forever? Maybe not. Here is the bargain: succeed three missions and you will gain your liberty. His Master allows him to explore his power, to unveil the secrets of the 1001 Nights. These missions are his Master's Three Wishes. But his magical Path won't be as easy as expected. Something worse than Death waits for him as he comes closer and closer to the True Nature of Arabian Magic...
name: The Assassin and The Lamp
